data.description: House is located is a nice quiet neighborhood, not far from highway’s access. About 25 min from Lake Nona, and 35 min from Melbourne Beach.  This property has lots of potential. Solar panels in working conditions,(owned.about $30,000value) enclose back porch and fenced patio with PVC fence. It has a water softener system. Ceramic tile throughout the house. Granite counter tops. Hurricane shutters in all windows. Overall condition is good, it just need a new owner to shine again.
